OL,3,CWorst delivery firms revealed as
OL,4,Cparcel problems reach record high
OL,6,FMore than 15 million people have
OL,7,Fexperienced a problem with their
OL,8,Flatest parcel delivery, as a record
OL,9,Fnumber of consumers are plagued with
OL,10,Fproblems receiving their orders, a new
OL,11,Fsurvey has found.
OL,13,FYodel came bottom of the league table,
OL,14,Ffailing to improve on last year's
OL,15,Franking of two stars out of five,
OL,16,Fwhile Royal Mail was top of the list
OL,17,Fwith 3.25 stars, Citizens Advice found.
