OL,3,CWorst delivery firms revealed as
OL,4,Cparcel problems reach record high
OL,6,FThe research, carried out over one
OL,7,Fmonth, reveals that the rate of parcel
OL,8,Fproblems remains at the highest levels
OL,9,Fseen in half a decade.
OL,11,FThe data was based on a survey of
OL,12,F8,000 UK adults between August and
OL,13,FSeptember this year.
OL,15,FWhere are the top delivery firms
OL,16,Franked?
OL,18,F1. Royal Mail - 3.25 stars
OL,20,F2. Amazon Logistics - 3 stars
