OL,3,CWorst delivery firms revealed as
OL,4,Cparcel problems reach record high
OL,6,FScores achieved by firms for
OL,7,Faccessibility worsened this year,
OL,8,Fdespite a new condition by Ofcom
OL,9,Frequiring firms to give disabled
OL,10,Fconsumers the opportunity to report
OL,11,Ftheir accessibility needs.
OL,13,FCitizens Advice's survey suggests that
OL,14,Fthree million people who have an
OL,15,Faccessibility need they would like to
OL,16,Fshare (37%) are still unable to share
OL,17,Fthese with firms.
