OL,3,CWorst delivery firms revealed as
OL,4,Cparcel problems reach record high
OL,6,FComplaints and customer service
OL,7,Frankings remained stagnant, with
OL,8,Falmost half (47%) of those who had
OL,9,Fexperienced a problem with their
OL,10,Fdelivery facing a further issue trying
OL,11,Fto resolve the problem, such as a slow
OL,12,Fresponse, issues with automated
OL,13,Fsystems, such as a chatbot and having
OL,14,Fto contact a firm multiple times to
OL,15,Fget a response.
