OL,3,CWorst delivery firms revealed as
OL,4,Cparcel problems reach record high
OL,6,FThe charity's chief executive Dame
OL,7,FClare Moriarty said: "Ofcom has passed
OL,8,Fthe parcel of responsibility for long
OL,9,Fenough. We've been doing the work of
OL,10,Fthe regulator for five years now by
OL,11,Fholding parcel companies to account
OL,12,Fand speaking up for consumers who are
OL,13,Fbearing the brunt of persistently poor
OL,14,Fservice."
OL,16,FAn Ofcom spokesman said it would
OL,17,Fcontinue to work with Citizens Advice
OL,18,Fto help consumers get a reliable
OL,19,Fdelivery service.
