OL,6,FThey continued: "We have a strong
OL,7,Ftrack record of holding parcel firms
OL,8,Fto account on behalf of the public.
OL,9,FThat has involved tracking people's
OL,10,Fexperiences of parcel deliveries for
OL,11,Fover a decade, and, as a result,
OL,12,Fintroducing strengthened regulations
OL,13,Fon parcel firms in 2023."
